               <scopecontent id="aspace_659337450da86b4ded82dba0a0cc4f2a">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Register to the collection.</p>
                  <p>Smith's application to the Yale School of Music. -- 1951</p>
                  <p>Smith's Yale registration form. -- 1952</p>
                  <p>Complete transcript of Smith's grades at Yale. -- 1956</p>
                  <p>Program for a concert including Smith's string quartet, Young Composers' Festival, Baltimore. -- 1956</p>
                  <p>Letter from Henry Cowell to Luther Noss praising Smith's involvement in the Young Composers' Festival. -- 1956</p>
                  <p>Program for a concert including Smith's Three Korean Songs, Yale. -- 1956</p>
                  <p>Smith's obituary in the New Haven Register. -- 1958</p>
                  <p>Letter from Smith's daughter, Hege Smith, reporting the death of her mother (Frank Smith's wife). -- 1973.</p>
               </scopecontent>
            </c>
